      <title>瑞典核心通胀放缓，为瑞典央行带来利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/sweden-s-core-inflation-slows-in-relief-for-the-riksbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典核心通胀率在年底的放缓幅度超过预期，引发人们对瑞典央行本月将实施计划中的一次降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/sweden-s-core-inflation-slows-in-relief-for-the-riksbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌预计 2024 年天然气收益将下降，因业绩不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司表示，其天然气销量下降，燃料交易收益下降，这是 2024 年各大能源公司业绩不佳的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
